{"word":"G1596 - ἑκουσίως - hekousíōs - hek-oo-see'-ose - Wilfully","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἑκουσίως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hekousíōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hek-oo-see'-ose</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wilfully</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மனப்பூர்வமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"voluntarily, willingly, of one's own accord"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from the same as <a href=\"#/G1595 - ἑκούσιον - hekoúsion - hek-oo'-see-on/1595\">G1595</a>; <i>voluntarily:</i> - wilfully, willingly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}